This high-powered warehouse is located at the rear of 37 Miles Street, Mulgrave and includes a private and secure access point. The property benefits from immediate access onto Springvale road, providing excellent access on the M1 Freeway and Princes Highway.

Property Features:
+ Warehouse of 750sqm* 
+ Secure yard of 420sqm* 
+ Office and amenity portables, paid monthly (optional) 
+ 300amp power capacity, with potential for more
+ Gross lease on offer
+ Flexible lease terms  

* approx

INVESTMENT SALE HIGHLIGHTS:
- Brand new 3x3 year lease to Argus Technologies
- Returning $95,000 net annually*
- 3.5% annual increases*
- 3 months security bond

Located in the heart of the hi-tech Monash precinct approximately 20km south-east of Melbourne's CBD. The building is easily accessible via the Monash Freeway, Eastlink and is well-serviced by a network of major roads including Springvale Road, Wellington Road and Princes Highway.

Argus Technologies have recently signed a new lease on the property. Key features of the property include a corporate office component, generous car park allocation and capability for growth which is what attracted the tenant to the property. Argus Technologies Pty Ltd a subsidiary of L+O Technologies, L+O Technologies has grown into one of the most successful, respected and trusted Electrical contracting Groups in the domestic building sector in Australia.

- Air conditioning over both levels
